        Respectful and Mindful Practices
      </p>
      <p>
        Please help us create a safe and welcoming event by following these guidelines:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Social Distancing: Respect social distancing requests from others, even if you know them.</li>
        <li>Self-Awareness: Understand your own health needs and take precautions based on your personal risk profile. </li>
