    </h2>
    <div class="content bod-text">
      <p class="h5">
        Ticket Transfers
      </p>
      <p>
        Tickets purchased for the CURE 2026 event are <b>non-transferable</b> under any circumstances.
      </p>
      <p>
        All registered attendees are required to undergo a background check at the time of ticket purchase. For this reason, transferring a ticket to another individual is not permitted, as it would bypass the required security screening.
      </p>
      <p>
        Event check-in procedures rely on attendee lists generated from the names of original ticket purchasers. Individuals whose names do not appear on the attendee list will be denied entry, regardless of possession of a ticket. This policy is strictly enforced to ensure the safety and security of all participants.
      </p>
      <p>
        Additionally, in the event of a sellout, a waiting list may be established. Unauthorized ticket transfers circumvent the fair and orderly process of this waitlist and will not be honored.
      </p>
      <p class="h5">
        Ticket Refunds
      </p>
      <p>
        Ticket holders may request a refund according to the schedule outlined below. All refunds are subject to a <b>$10 processing fee</b> to cover administrative and transaction costs.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><b>100% Refund</b> (minus processing fee): Requests made on or before <b>October 3, 2025</b></li>
        <li><b>75% Refund</b> (minus processing fee): Requests made between <b>October 4 and October 31, 2025</b></li>
        <li><b>50% Refund</b> (minus processing fee): Requests made between <b>November 1 and November 28, 2025</b></li>
        <li><b>No Refunds:</b> Requests made on or after <b>November 29, 2025</b></li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        All refund requests must be submitted in writing via email to <a href="mailto:admin@kicevents.com">admin@kicevents.com.</a>
      </p>
      <p class="h5">
        On-Site Policy
      </p>
      <p>
        No one will be permitted to enter the CURE 2026 Event Space without advance registration.
      </p>
      <p>
        There will be no ticket sales, exchanges, substitutions, refunds, or transfers at the event site under any circumstances.
